    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5bu1gvholjbm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
      "text": "1. Cold Launch",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5b7wq77rwyal",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u2022 App icon \u2192 splash\n\u2022 No Fitz persisted (@State only,\n  per D-2026-05-19-002, Casey M7)\n\u2022 No lastUV? jump to disclaimer\n\u2022 Has cached UV? still gated by L1",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5bf9wxxdq22h",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFCDD2",
      "strokeColor": "#C62828",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5cjkaj24dla8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "2. L1 Disclaimer (.fullScreenCover)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.248Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.248Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dtraol2y90e8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u2022 Title: \"How accurate is this for you?\"\n\u2022 Body + \u26a0\ufe0f glyph (Donatello M1)\n\u2022 Children-line on its own row\n\u2022 Inline \"see About\" \u2192 notForMe anchor\n\u2022 Photosensitizer line above the fold\n\u2022 Button: \"I understand\" (single CTA)\n\u2022 Re-fires EVERY cold launch\n\u2022 NO \"Don't Show Again\"",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dlhdp80fvoh",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#E3F2FD",
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5d1f1uvhgv1ky",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "text": "3. Skin-Type Picker (Fitz)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dw0mzqefr9oe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u2022 Header: \"Pick the row that matches\n  what your skin DOES, not its color\"\n\u2022 Rows I\u2013VI, each \u226556pt tap target\n\u2022 \u274c NO default selection (D-...-012)\n\u2022 \u274c NO skin-tone swatches (MMT-3)\n\u2022 Wheeler edited variant copy:\n  I \"Very fair\u2026\", II \"Fair\u2026\", III\n  \"Medium tone\u2026\", IV \"Light-brown\u2026\",\n  V \"Brown\u2026 rarely burns\", VI\n  \"Deeply pigmented\u2026 never burns\"\n\u2022 Cite in About: NCBI NBK481857 +\n  Fitzpatrick 1988 (paraphrase only,\n  D-2026-05-19-009 \u2705)\n\u2022 @State only \u2014 never @AppStorage",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5egte08kezq",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#E3F2FD",
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e4og5d8reh48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "text": "4. Location Permission",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5etv07gv3ear",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u2022 Inline rationale BEFORE iOS prompt\n\u2022 \"When-In-Use\" only (never \"Always\")\n\u2022 Privacy line: \"Coords rounded to\n  2 decimals, never leave device\"\n\u2022 Primary CTA: \"Use my location\"\n  in .safeAreaInset(.bottom) \u2014 thumb\n\u2022 On deny \u2192 graceful empty state,\n  not error string. Re-tap path.\n\u2022 Required because WeatherKit needs\n  location for currentWeather UV\n  (D-2026-05-19-003)\n\u2022 SPF picker also shown here (chip\n  row, neutral, default SPF 30)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5ez3aezuhn8ip",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF9C4",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5eojgeoarwgol",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1360,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "5. Photo-Sens Awareness",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e6h9xvprcytq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1360,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u26a0 NOT a separate screen \u2014 three\n   surfaces (per Wheeler \u00a77.3):\n\n(a) Inside L1 modal (step 2):\n    inline \"see About\" \u2192 notForMe\n(b) L3 link on verdict card (next):\n    \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n(c) L4 About section, anchor =\n    notForMe (Wheeler-authored)\n\n\u274c NO \"I'm photosensitive\" toggle\n   (zero special-category data,\n   per Raphael Art.9 / Casey M7)\n\u274c NO brand drug names \u2014 generics\n   only (Plunder)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e3klzbaya22u",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1660,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#C8E6C9",
      "strokeColor": "#1B5E20",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5epkv4k0keaej",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#1B5E20",
      "text": "6. First Verdict \u2193 Main",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e0wbu6tlhqb2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "\u2022 Hero number animates in\n  (.contentTransition(.numericText))\n\u2022 Tier badge color+shape+symbol\n\u2022 L2 footer becomes visible\n\u2022 L3 link \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n  becomes reachable\n\u2022 WeatherKit lockup visible\n\u2022 Success haptic (.sensoryFeedback)\n\u2022 Lands on NowView (= Main Screen\n  below, in LANE 2)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
