    {
      "id": "mpcd8jp77i0qzzhiv13",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 920,
      "y": 725,
      "strokeColor": "#01579B",
      "text": "INPUTS  +  TIMER (TimelineView)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.411Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.411Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd8jp78tait81cyo4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 920,
      "y": 755,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "DisclosureGroup(\"Inputs\") \u2014 collapsed by\ndefault; auto-expanded at AX4+.\n\n  \u25b8 Skin type  \u2192  SkinTypeView (Fitz I-VI)\n  \u25b8 SPF        \u2192  Picker(.menu)  None/15/30/50/70+\n  \u25b8 Use my location  (.safeAreaInset.bottom)\n                     primary thumb-zone CTA\n\nTimelineView(.periodic(from:.now, by: 60))\n  \u00b7 Updates hero number every minute\n  \u00b7 Pure subtraction from snapshot estimate\n  \u00b7 No background fetch in v1\n\nPull-to-refresh on ScrollView re-fetches UV.\n\nHaptic on tier crossing (.warning) \u2014\ntrail-run / open-water swimmer needs the\nphysical nudge when window elapses.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.411Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.411Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd8jp77mjcchzsc1e",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80,
