      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd8jp8pd2pscm0xap",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1245,
      "strokeColor": "#880E4F",
      "text": "\u2699 SETTINGS / ABOUT entry  (gearshape in nav bar \u2192 SettingsSheet \u2192 AboutView, where L4 lives)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.412Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.412Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd8jp9ptb6te13zdc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1270,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "SettingsSheet (.sheet, .presentationDetents([.medium, .large])):\n  \u25b8 Skin & SPF  \u25b8 About & Citations  \u2192  AboutView (L4, the source of truth)  \u25b8 Attribution & Legal  \u25b8 Restore Purchase\n\nAboutView anchors (ScrollViewReader):  howItWorks  \u00b7  notForMe  (L3 destination \u2014 Wheeler-authored \"When this estimate may not apply\")  \u00b7  weatherWhy  \u00b7\n                                       citations  \u00b7  weatherData  \u00b7  privacy  \u00b7  pricing  \u00b7  outdoorTip   \u2014 anchor-linkable so deep-links land precisely.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.413Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:23:16.413Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlzsw3gt89a88",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1480,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFE0B2",
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "LANE 3 \u2014 KEY BRANCH POINTS  &  ANNOTATIONS  (where the design materially differs from a na\u00efve flow)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlwz121iottf",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlrgkbkxb8dg9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1555,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 NO-DEFAULT FITZPATRICK  (D-2026-05-19-012)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydl9xc4m79vso8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Prototype pre-selected Fitz III; iOS does NOT.\nUser MUST tap a row before the verdict renders.\n\nWHY:  defaulting to III silently inflates the\nestimated safe time for Type I/II users by\n~50%  (MED_III / MED_I = 300/200 = 1.5\u00d7).\nThat is a one-way safety error.\n\nEmpty SkinType is a first-class state on\nNowView (\"Pick a skin type to see your\nestimate\"). Anchoring (Tversky & Kahneman\n1974) is real and asymmetric \u2014 over-estimating\nsafe time \u2192 erythema \u2192 melanoma risk.\n\nConvergent signal: Suchi + Linka + Wheeler.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlaulupv1sapm",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 240,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 580,
      "height": -1080,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlov1igddujak",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 460,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlekr5d9n0l9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1555,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 L1 STICKY + PHOTO-SENS REACH-BACK",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlw7ipxxqdu5f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "L1 modal re-fires every cold launch\n(Donatello M1).  NO \"Don't Show Again.\"\n\nThe L1 surface is NOT load-bearing alone\nfor the high-risk persona (Accutane/lupus):\nthey modal-blind on cold launch & need to\nreach the photo-sens caveat mid-task.\n\n\u2192 L3 link on verdict card is additive\n   (deep-links to L4 `notForMe`).\n\u2192 Footer \u24d8 About is also tappable.\n\nD-2026-05-19-007 + D-2026-05-19-011.\nSkill: persona-keyed-disclaimer-visibility.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlr48kg2z9ym",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 650,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": -150,
      "height": -1080,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlj69n4b318z9",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 860,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlduy5rdphhht",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1555,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udccc  240-MINUTE DISPLAY CAP",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.089Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmv0wmutvqq3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "If model output \u2265 240 minutes, the hero\nDISPLAYS \"240+ min\" (= \"4+ hours\") rather\nthan the literal integer.\n\nWHY:  Fitz V/VI + SPF 70 + low UV can yield\n\"480 min\" \u2014 mathematically right but\nbehaviorally misleading (implies a literal\n8-hour safe stretch, which the model is\nnot validated to claim).\n\nInternal calculation is unchanged. Display\nclamp only. VoiceOver mirrors the cap.\n\nSource: Suchi \u00a71.8 \u2192 Linka spec \u00a73.3.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmrbpt0uzme9p",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 1050,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": -770,
      "height": -660,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmjc2ksatde6q",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1260,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmqlvvre36lx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1275,
      "y": 1555,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udccc  WEATHERKIT ATTRIBUTION ALWAYS VISIBLE",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmub5yrkj4mo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1275,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Apple's WeatherKit T&C requires the\n\" Weather\" lockup wherever data is shown,\n+ tappable link to\nweatherkit.apple.com/legal-attribution.html\n\nSurfaces:\n  \u00b7 Below verdict card on NowView (always)\n  \u00b7 Full lockup in About \u2192 Weather data\n  \u00b7 Dedicated AttributionView screen\n\n\u274c REMOVE Open-Meteo CC BY 4.0 footer\n   from all iOS surfaces (web keeps it).\n\nD-2026-05-19-002/003/004 \u2014 launch BLOCKER\nif missing. Apple review will reject.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmw544aqc0mwe",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 1450,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": -1160,
      "height": -480,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:24:22.090Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatinfus2ksvumh7",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1770,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.447Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatiop5rm0k8gu2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1785,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udccc  L3 \"Is this estimate for me?\" DEEP-LINK",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatioez8aqnmhojc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Suchi-named L3 pattern. Inline link on verdict\ncard; deep-links to AboutView with anchor =\n`notForMe`. Uses ScrollViewReader.proxy.scrollTo\nwith .animation(.smooth) \u2014 honors Reduce Motion.\n\nVoiceOver label MUST spell out the destination:\n\"Is this estimate for me? Opens About,\nconditions and medications that may affect\nthis estimate.\"\n\nNOT a way to soften L1. NOT a \"Don't Show\nAgain\" loophole. ADDITIVE to L1, not a replacement.\n\nPersona served: Accutane, lupus, vitiligo,\nalbinism, pregnancy, post-procedure cohort.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatiopj9kehzeqga",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 250,
      "y": 1770,
      "width": -30,
      "height": -790,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatiola4j4h7lbyd",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 460,
      "y": 1770,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF59D",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatiotetwihbk2l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1785,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\u2696\ufe0f  PLUNDER's 8 PRE-SUBMIT FLAGS  (non-blocking)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcdatiogojdv1mbwma",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Eight items Plunder wants attorney sign-off\non before App Store submit (don't block design):\n\n 1. NCBI citation wording in About\n 2. \"Apple Weather\" vs \" Weather\" body prose\n 3. L1 modal final copy (Donatello M1 verbatim?)\n 4. L3 link copy: \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n 5. SPF chip neutrality (no \"recommended\" badge)\n 6. Privacy paragraph wording\n 7. Pricing claim: \"no subscription ever\"\n 8. Banned phrases audit (port from prototype JS)\n\nSurfaces affected:  L1 modal, verdict card,\nSkinTypeView footer, AboutView all sections,\nAttributionView, App Store description.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:02.448Z",
      "version": 1
