      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s2s9ise196cnh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 2298,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "P3  DEVON\nPCT thru-hike\nr/PacificCrestTr\nFitz I",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.418Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.418Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s2bn0x2nrbc1e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 215,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "~10\u201315 sec STICKY.\nDoing gear-weight\nmath. Reads whole\ndisclaimer. Will not\ntap inline link (not\nphoto-sens'd). May\nscreenshot.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.418Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.418Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s34nt2fnuuado",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 465,
      "y": 2290,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFEBEE",
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3nvyytc7tld",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "\u2605 THE NO-DEFAULT VALIDATOR \u2605\nPicks Fitz I. Self-quote: \"I got\na sunburn on a somewhat sunny\nday in February in NYC.\" Without\nthe no-default rule, defaulting\nto III would under-estimate his\nburn risk ~50% on first launch.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3y1h6t7dyd9e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "\u26a0 BRANCH: planning\nat home in Feb. No\ncurrent useful location.\nDenied \u2192 graceful\nempty state. v1 has\nno \"plan-for-elsewhere\"\naffordance (v1.1).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s343z2r4ultyl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "Multi-scenarios:\nFitz I \u00d7 SPF 30 \u00d7 UV 9\n= \"Short\". Fitz I \u00d7\nSPF 50 = still short.\nValidates \"240+ min\"\ncap never kicks in\nfor him. No L3 tap.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3fxirnme2l5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "JTBD: scenario\nplanning. v1.1 should\nship \"try different\nUV/location\" affordance.\nv1: uses iOS Simulator\nas workaround.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s31dejhsyyp5s",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "Reads at rest stop,\nrecalc, continues.\nHis burn-time is short\nenough that elapsed\nstate fires frequently.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
