      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3kxakaup7lz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 2398,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "P4  ASHA\nAccutane patient\nr/Accutane\nFitz IV",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3iobd5r65hz",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 210,
      "y": 2390,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#F3E5F5",
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s35rh5bi7anio",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "\u2605 LOAD-BEARING \u2605  30\u201360 sec dwell.\nSees photo-sens line \u2192 TAPS \"see About\"\ninline \u2192 AboutView opens at notForMe\nanchor (on top of L1) \u2192 reads cohort list\n\u2192 recognizes \"retinoids\" = her Accutane\n\u2192 dismisses \u2192 returns to L1 \u2192 \"I understand\"\nTHIS IS THE VISIBILITY LOOP (not attestation).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3yla4bzh9r2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Picks Fitz IV (her\nactual phototype).\nRE-READS footer:\n\"assumes healthy skin\n+ no photo-sens meds\"\n\u2014 even though she\nalready saw L1.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3witigs1b6gs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Reads privacy \u00b6\n(medical-privacy\nposture). Grants\nreluctantly. Never\n\"Always\" location.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3xi15364uuk",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 985,
      "y": 2390,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#F3E5F5",
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s396iis1d7hmw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "\u2605 MOST IMPORTANT L3 TAP IN THE APP \u2605\nVerdict reads \"120 min\" but lived\nexp says ~20 min. TAPS L3 \"Is this\nestimate for me?\" \u2192 AboutView notForMe.\nMentally divides 120 by 4\u20136. Quote:\n\"UV maybe 3 and it looks like I've\nrolled a few. What can I do to stop this?\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3ybeuwqinfp9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "\u2605 L1 re-fires every\ncold launch = HER\nre-attestation surface\nwhen meds change.\nWhy Donatello M1 says\nNO \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3ubvx4a9s7th",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Probably indoors by\nthis point (her cohort\nburns at 5 min of\ngardening). Reads\nelapsed copy as\nratification.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5zlwwl0w4ghp",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 2490,
      "width": 140,
      "height": 88,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFE0B2",
      "strokeColor": "#EF6C00",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5bzf8q1pnfp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 2498,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "P5  TOM\u00c1S\ntrail runner\nr/trailrunning\nFitz IV/V",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5py3ztuzq56d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 215,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "~2 sec RISK.\nOne earbud in, at\ntrailhead. Dismisses\nwithout reading.\nL2 footer must\ndo real work for\nhim every screen.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5g0ro78ujv3b",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 465,
      "y": 2490,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF3E0",
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5oyk9cjpcr3c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "\u26a0 UNDER-PICK RISK\nActually Fitz IV. Self-narrative\n\"I tan, I don't burn\" may push\nhim to Type V/VI. Behavior-first\nrow copy is PARTIAL mitigation \u2014\nhe reads \"rarely burns\" on V and\nself-selects on that clause alone.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5gul9ewdir2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Mid-stride tap. Grants.\nButton MUST visibly\nrespond (spinner /\nlocation.fill swap) \u2014\n~2-5 sec fetch feels\nlike eternity in motion.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5xsp0iqdn0m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Reads TWO things:\nthe integer + tier color.\nEverything else is\nwasted screen real estate.\nSaccade does NOT reach\nthe L3 link.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s52g2afy2x4yt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Set app down at\ntrailhead. Now at\nmile 8. Hasn't looked\nat phone. Repeating-\nuse = nothing yet \u2014\nuntil window elapses.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s565axfzd3lut",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1505,
      "y": 2490,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF3E0",
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5umarfteoej",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "\u2605 HIS SAFETY MOMENT \u2605\nWindow-elapsed: hero swaps\nto \ud83d\udee1 + warning haptic. THE\nWHOLE APP IS JUSTIFIED BY\nTHIS STATE FIRING CORRECTLY\nFOR HIM. Verify haptic +\nvisual contrast in direct sun.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    }
